                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <locus target="#iv(erso)"/>
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                      Concluding Hymn for the Synaxarium and the Homiliary miracles for the archangel Mika’el.
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለዘአቅረብኩ: ማኅሌተ: አዘኪርየ: አዕላፈ። እምዕለ: ተፀምዱከ: ዘልፈ። ለለይትነበብ: ተወከፍ: ዘንዴትየ: መጽሐፈ። እንተ ረሰይከ: እግዚኦ: ፀሪቀ: መበለት: ውኩፈ። <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#116v"/>
                    <desc type="Asmat">
                    Asmat prayer to ward off Satan, copied for Wäldä Mäsqäl and for Wälättä Gäbriel
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ አብ: ወወልድ <gap reason="omitted"/> በዘይቀርበከ: ሰይጣን: ዘንተ: ድግም: በዕናኤል: በኤትናኤል: በእምሩኤል: ወበርስያሄል: ያማስ: ያርዘማውታ: ናውል: ሕንኤል: በዘቆመ: ሰማይ: ወምድር: መርሜር:<gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <locus target="#117r"/>
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    A prohecy by Wäldä Mäsqäl regarding the king, in Amharic.
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="am">ዝ: ትእምርት: ዘወልደ: መስቀል: በሃይማኖት: ክርክር: ምክር: አልሰማሉ: በካህናት: እከይ: ይጠፋሉ: <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <locus target="#33v #34r"/>
                    <desc>
                    The image is missing
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <desc>
                    Each month has a note beside the title of the month in Amharic explaining the archangel’s mission
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <locus target="#115v"/>
                    <desc>
                    Colophon: commissioned by ?, name erased and replaced by Wäldä Mäsqäl. Copied by Sǝdakyal. The commissioner solicits prayer.
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e3">
                    <locus target="#115v"> col. 2</locus>
                    <desc>
                    The days of the year when the heavens are open to receive prayer
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <locus target="#iv(erso)"> and passim</locus>
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    Secondary owners: Wäldä Mäsqäl and Wälättä Gabriel
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a6">
                    <locus target="#117r"> upper left</locus>
                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">
                    Note of ownership by Wälättä Gabriel
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <locus target="#117v"/>
                    <desc>
                    The owner, Wälättä Gabriel, solicits prayer, in Amharic, by people who use the book
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#9 #36 #101"/>
                    <desc>
                    Navigation system:
                    black yarn sewn into the fore edge  to mark content;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <desc>
                    marginal notation to mark readings
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e7">
                    <locus target="#8r #8v #34v #68v #70r"/>
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention:
                    (etc.) words of text are written interlinearly;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e8">
                    <locus target="#39r"> col. 2, line 12</locus>
                    <desc>
                    and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted;
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e9">
                    <locus target="#12r #20r #42r #43r"/>
                    <desc>
                    (etc.) text has been removed
                    </desc>
                    </item>
